OL,3,CAttempted murder arrest after man shot
OL,4,Cin Cotswolds town
OL,6,FA man has been arrested on suspicion
OL,7,Fof attempted murder after another man
OL,8,Fin his thirties was reportedly shot in
OL,9,Fa Cotswolds town.
OL,11,FPolice say they were called to
OL,12,FButler's Field, in Lechlade,
OL,13,FGloucestershire, at around 7:10pm on
OL,14,FMonday, 20 April, following a report
OL,15,Fthat a man had shot another man who
OL,16,Fwas sitting stationary in his vehicle.
OL,18,FInvestigating officers said the victim
OL,19,Fmanaged to drive a short distance and
OL,20,Fget inside a property after the attack.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
