FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1776780668
OL,3,CAttempted murder arrest after man shot
OL,4,Cin Cotswolds town
OL,6,FHe was later taken to hospital with
OL,7,Fsuspected gunshot wounds, which are
OL,8,Fnot thought to be life-threatening,
OL,9,Fthe force said.
OL,11,FArmed police and the police helicopter
OL,12,Fwere called out, and a man in his
OL,13,Ftwenties was arrested in Fairford
OL,14,Fshortly before 10pm on suspicion of
OL,15,Fattempted murder. He remains in police
OL,16,Fcustody.
OL,18,FInvestigating officers said a firearm
OL,19,Fwas recovered at the scene.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
