FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1776780668
OL,3,CAttempted murder arrest after man shot
OL,4,Cin Cotswolds town
OL,6,FActing Detective Inspector Sophie
OL,7,FDawkins from Gloucestershire Police's
OL,8,FCriminal Investigation Department
OL,9,Fsaid: "This is a worrying incident,
OL,10,Fand no doubt will have caused a lot of
OL,11,Fconcern in the community, especially
OL,12,Fduring the time while officers were
OL,13,Fsearching for the suspect.
OL,15,F"We're in the early stages of an
OL,16,Finvestigation, and at this time, it is
OL,17,Funderstood that those involved are
OL,18,Fknown to each other, and we're not
OL,19,Flooking for anyone else in connection
OL,20,Fwith the incident.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
