FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1776780668
OL,3,CAttempted murder arrest after man shot
OL,4,Cin Cotswolds town
OL,6,F"Those living nearby will see an
OL,7,Fenhanced police presence over the
OL,8,Fcoming days, and we'd encourage anyone
OL,9,Fwith concerns to speak to officers in
OL,10,Fthe area."
OL,12,FAnyone with information about the
OL,13,Fincident or anyone who has any
OL,14,Fdashcam, CCTV or mobile phone footage
OL,15,Fis being urged to contact
OL,16,FGloucestershire Police.
